15:52.518 --> 15:55.988 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: So, on balance,
would you say
Iran is more helpful in the
fight against

15:56.022 --> 15:57.890 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
