to do more. I think they have
done some things,

16:00.560 --> 16:07.133 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
but they need to demonstrate
their commitment
to helping defeat these
terrorist organizations

16:07.166 --> 16:12.805 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
