23:00.613 --> 23:03.849 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Michael
Thompson is executive
director of the Council of State
Governments

23:03.882 --> 23:09.054 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
