going to
say, well, they need an
education.

23:17.263 --> 23:21.533 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So I think everybody assumes
they get a certain
quality of education while
they're incarcerated.

23:21.567 --> 23:26.538 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
