public education
system is.

23:29.341 --> 23:33.812 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: His group
found large gaps
from state to state in education
available

23:33.846 --> 23:39.785 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
