states, Massachusetts
centralizes juvenile education,
rather than

24:20.459 --> 24:23.696 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
spreading it among state, local
and private
agencies.

24:23.729 --> 24:27.499 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I'm assuming some of these young
these kids
