crimes.

24:27.533 --> 24:29.368 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
LYNNE ALLEN: They are.

24:29.401 --> 24:36.375 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
This facility works with young
men up to manslaughter
charges. So we do have some kids
who have

24:36.408 --> 24:40.579 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
