24:42.348 --> 24:46.719 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: In 2015,
17-year-old Josh
was convicted of manslaughter.
He's spent

24:46.752 --> 24:51.991 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
the past 10 months at Connelly
and has another
eight to go.

24:52.024 --> 24:57.062 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Like the other 14 young men
here, he lives
on a secure detention floor, his
movement

24:57.096 --> 25:05.871 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
