let them down,
or myself down, for that matter.

26:08.000 --> 26:12.104 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
LYNNE ALLEN: They're coming back
to communities.
We want these kids to come out
with the skills

26:12.137 --> 26:17.409 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
