each student into and out of
this system,

26:29.254 --> 26:34.326 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
making sure education plans,
grades and credits
transfer from and back to
school.

26:34.359 --> 26:41.366 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MICHAEL THOMPSON: When a kid who
is incarcerated,
they are going to get out, and
