transition.

27:02.087 --> 27:06.859 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Education and
career counselor
Kelly McMorrow works with Josh
and about 75

27:06.892 --> 27:09.328 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
