27:24.409 --> 27:26.912 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
KELLY MCMORROW, Education and
Career Counselor:
It's challenging, but I think
that's our biggest

27:26.945 --> 27:31.450 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
