28:13.825 --> 28:17.629 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Back in
Lowell, 20-year-old
John Coady estimates that he
lived in nearly

28:17.663 --> 28:23.302 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
