28:26.572 --> 28:33.745 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN COADY, Resident: Being
locked up, you
lose a lot of life experiences
where you gain

28:33.779 --> 28:35.547 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
