28:35.581 --> 28:39.251 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
And if you can get your
education in there,
like, at least you will have
something going

28:39.284 --> 28:44.489 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
for you. If you don't have
education or work
experience, or anything, I mean,
you're lost.

28:44.523 --> 28:48.694 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
When you come out, you're going
to have no
friends. You're going -- your
family is probably

28:48.727 --> 28:53.298 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
not going to care much. You're
not going to
have anything.

28:53.332 --> 28:57.903 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: And many say
that's a prospect
still far too many young people
across the

28:57.936 --> 28:59.871 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
nation continue to face.

28:59.905 --> 29:02.774 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
